MATCH_TOOL: Write
MATCH_PATTERN: \.superpowers/brainstorm/.*/content/.*\.html
ADVISORY: |
  The brainstorm visual companion server dies frequently (often well before the 30-min timeout).
  Before writing content, check that $STATE_DIR/server-info exists. If the server has restarted,
  you'll need to: (1) restart with start-server.sh, (2) note the NEW port and session directory,
  (3) copy or rewrite content to the new session's content/ directory. The old session's files
  are orphaned. Always tell the user the updated URL after a restart.
